<div class="row">
  <div class="medium-6 small-12 columns">
    <h3><strong>Why Do We Evangelize?</strong></h3>
    <p class="indent">Jesus, in his divine strategy, left the work of spreading the good news of salvation to his disciples, training them to become “fishers of men” (Matthew 4:19), and sending them to “make disciples of all nations” (Matthew 28:19). Evangelism is also an essential mark of the Spirit-empowered disciple, as being filled with the Holy Spirit precedes the work of witnessing (Acts 1:8).</p>
